    "The multi-head attention mechanism is then built upon several parallel self-attention heads:",
    "where,, are learned projection matrices for each head, and is the output projection matrix.",
    "The two main components of Transformers are encoders and decoders.",
    "Encoders extract and comprehend relevant information from input text using self-attention, while decoders generate translated text using the embeddings from the encoder (Fu et al., 2023).",
    "The encoder block combines multi-head self-attention and feed-forward neural networks."
